
v1.2.0

	* Internal API to send messages to players; players are given
	  a welcome message when they connect
	* Some bug fixes; OpenGL works properly where it was broken in
	  a few places before.

v1.1.0

	* Bugfixes.
	* IPv6 support
	* Rocks exploding now give a pretty red circle explosion effect.
	* Ruby-based mirroring relay server
	* Screen rotate turned off by default

v1.0.0

	* Initial release.

